  "description" : "http://anidb.net/ch151825 [Nonoyama Fuu] - an innocent elementary school student very excited for Summer Vacation. http://anidb.net/ch151824 [Nonoyama Rui] - a modest, hard-working Junior High School Student.\nTwo sisters that only recently have become distant from each other... One day, Fuu encountered a mysterious spaceship and received magical powers. Rui also had received magical powers. Fuu and Rui transform into the grown-up versions they wish to be. However, there are two rules: You will only have magical powers for one year and No one should know about your magical powers. The two of them did not know each other`s secret! Each of them will become idols!\nSource: Bandai Namco Filmworks",
